# StudyFill Git Rules

## Branch Strategy

Two long-lived branches:

| Branch | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `main` | Production / deployment |
| `develop` | Active development integration |

Flow:

```txt
develop → feat/fix/refactor/... → PR → develop
develop → (release) → PR → main
```

Rules:

- Start all feature work from `develop`
- Branch off: `feat/*`, `fix/*`, `refactor/*`, etc.
- Merge feature branches back into `develop` via PR
- Deploy by merging `develop` into `main` (not feature branches directly into `main`)

## When to Act

- Create commits **only when explicitly requested**
- Push and create PRs **only when explicitly requested**
- Default PR base branch: `develop` (use `main` only for release/deploy PRs)

## Branch Naming

```
<type>/<scope>-<short-kebab-description>
```

Examples:

```txt
feat/blank-study-answer-check
fix/auth-empty-input
refactor/pdf-workspace-layout
chore/deps-update-next
```

## Allowed Types

`feat`, `fix`, `refactor`, `chore`, `docs`, `test`

## Allowed Scopes

Match feature folders: `auth`, `dashboard`, `pdf`, `explanation`, `blank-study`, `ui`, `lib`, `deps`

## Commit Title (required)

```
<type>(<scope>): <imperative verb phrase, lowercase, no period>
```

Examples:

```txt
feat(dashboard): add pdf list section
feat(blank-study): implement answer checking
refactor(pdf): separate workspace layout
fix(auth): handle empty input validation
```

- Title language: **English**

## Commit Body

**Small fix** (single file, obvious change): title only

**All other commits** — include body in this format:

```markdown
## Summary
- 변경 내용 1~3줄

## Why
- 변경이 필요한 이유 (1줄)

## Test plan
- [ ] 확인 항목
```

- Body language: **Korean**

## Pull Request

Use `gh pr create`. PR title matches commit title (or a summary title if multiple commits).

**Base branch:**

- Feature/fix/refactor PRs → target `develop`
- Release/deploy PRs → target `main` (source: `develop`)

PR body template:

```markdown
## Summary
- 이 PR이 하는 일 (1~3 bullets)

## Changes
- 변경된 파일/기능 단위 설명

## Test plan
- [ ] 확인 항목
- [ ] 확인 항목

## Screenshots
<!-- UI 변경 시 첨부, 해당 없으면 N/A -->
N/A
```

- PR body language: **Korean**
- PR title language: **English**

## Workflow Order

When asked to commit and open a PR:

1. Ensure `develop` is up to date (`git checkout develop && git pull`)
2. Create and switch to feature branch from `develop`
3. Stage relevant files (never commit secrets: `.env`, credentials)
4. Commit with formatted message
5. Push with `-u origin HEAD` if new branch
6. Create PR against `develop`

For release/deploy (only when explicitly requested):

1. Create PR from `develop` into `main`
2. PR title example: `release: merge develop into main`

## Examples

**Commit:**

```txt
feat(blank-study): add inline answer checking with feedback

## Summary
- 빈칸 입력 후 정답/오답 피드백 UI 추가
- 오답 시 재시도 버튼 노출

## Why
- active recall 학습 플로우의 핵심 상호작용 구현

## Test plan
- [ ] 정답 제출 시 success 상태 확인
- [ ] 오답 제출 시 retry 버튼 동작 확인
```

**PR title:** `feat(blank-study): add inline answer checking with feedback`
